594
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:07,000
to release Gou.

595
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:09,480
I'll also tell him about
the Divine Blade Sect.

596
00:27:10,510 --> 00:27:11,430
Senior,

597
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:13,110
