598
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:15,870
I'm sure the chairman will like you.

599
00:27:16,510 --> 00:27:18,070
We'll work together

600
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:19,630
to restore the honor of our sect!

601
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:30,120
Junior.

602
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:33,750
Senior.

603
00:27:40,030 --> 00:27:41,760
Are you really leaving?

604
00:27:43,350 --> 00:27:45,080
Are you really not going to save me?

605
00:27:45,590 --> 00:27:47,240
At least talk with me for a while.

606
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,480
I can't believe it.

607
00:27:54,700 --> 00:27:55,700
