611
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:04,160
Get the Rockblade
and complete your mission.

612
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,190
You nasty rascal!

613
00:28:05,750 --> 00:28:07,190
You fooled me!

614
00:28:07,350 --> 00:28:08,910
You only want the blade.

615
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:10,870
How dare you come here?

616
00:28:11,070 --> 00:28:12,750
Today, Swallow and I will show you

617
00:28:12,750 --> 00:28:14,350
the true power of the Divine Blade Sect.

618
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:15,870
Ridiculous.

619
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:18,270
Look how fat you are.

620
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:20,760
The Divine Blade Sect
is not what it used to be.

621
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,280
None of you

622
00:28:22,510 --> 00:28:25,040
deserve to wield the Rockblade.

623
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:26,630
If you're smart,

624
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:28,190
give it to me now,

625
00:28:29,030 --> 00:28:30,760
and I'll spare your lives.

626
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:32,560
Mr. Dao,

627
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,350
you deceived me!

628
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:36,960
I'll kill you!

629
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:44,830
