630
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,720
Crane Knight?

631
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:53,960
Want to lure me out?

632
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,430
Stop dreaming.

633
00:29:40,590 --> 00:29:42,040
Before you die,

634
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:43,630
I'll tell you a secret.

635
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:48,350
I was the one who killed the Blade God.

636
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:53,040
Go to hell!

637
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:58,590
Lifetime Strike!

638
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:05,870
Senior!

639
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:07,350
Senior!

640
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:08,630
Senior!

641
00:30:09,070 --> 00:30:09,920
Senior!

642
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:11,080
Hang in there!

643
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:12,190
Senior!

644
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:14,000
Junior...

645
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:16,870
It was him.

646
00:30:17,510 --> 00:30:18,910
It was him.

647
00:30:20,510 --> 00:30:22,720
