659
00:31:02,270 --> 00:31:03,560
No… Senior!

660
00:31:03,750 --> 00:31:04,870
No, Senior!

661
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:08,190
You can't leave me!

662
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,560
Senior!

663
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:11,240
Senior!

664
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:16,630
Back then,

665
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:20,040
the second lady of the Silk Manor and I

666
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:23,560
