667
00:31:23,720 --> 00:31:24,670
I know.

668
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:26,150
I know...

669
00:31:27,510 --> 00:31:28,430
Senior.

670
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,080
Senior...

671
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,320
Stop talking.

672
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:33,150
I don't want to see you suffer.

673
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,560
Over the years,

674
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:40,630
I've been blinded by hatred

675
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:44,800
and missed too much.

676
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:49,080
If I have a second chance,

677
00:31:50,510 --> 00:31:53,110
I will definitely find the second lady.

678
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,360
Junior.

679
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:03,110
Don't try to steal her from me.

680
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:06,080
Senior.

681
00:32:06,830 --> 00:32:08,350
Are you deceiving me?

682
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:11,240
Don't set me up like this!

683
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:13,680
It's not too late to see a doctor!

684
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,240
- Let's go!
- Don't worry.

685
00:32:17,110 --> 00:32:18,040
After all,

686
00:32:19,110 --> 00:32:21,430
I'm the Blade God's disciple.

687
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:25,430
How could that rascal kill me so easily?

688
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:50,390
It's you.

689
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:52,760
Leader!

690
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,510
Who's your leader?

691
00:32:55,510 --> 00:32:57,080
Stop talking nonsense.

692
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:58,190
Leader.

693
00:32:58,510 --> 00:33:00,310
Kill Crane Knight

694
00:33:00,310 --> 00:33:01,510
and take the Rockblade,

695
00:33:01,510 --> 00:33:04,480
and we'll be able to
revitalize the divine sect!

696
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:05,590
I've told you a million times

697
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:07,040
I'm not the sect leader!

698
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:10,110
I'm Gou Lingfeng, an Ox-rank hero
of the Martial Artists

699
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:11,030
Association!

700
00:33:11,030 --> 00:33:12,030
Lingfeng,

701
00:33:12,030 --> 00:33:13,200
he killed my father

702
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,480
and injured Swallow.

703
00:33:15,510 --> 00:33:17,320
Did you kill the Blade God?

704
00:33:17,750 --> 00:33:20,200
Did you turn Crane and Swallow
against each other

705
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:22,520
and try to use the Blade Tomb
to revitalize the demonic sect?

706
00:33:24,350 --> 00:33:25,480
Do you really

707
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:29,630
want to let Gui Lao down?

708
00:33:30,030 --> 00:33:31,480
Who cares about that old man?

709
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:33,760
He screwed me over.

710
00:33:34,790 --> 00:33:36,520
If that old man weren't

711
00:33:37,030 --> 00:33:38,270
too hesitant

712
00:33:38,270 --> 00:33:39,720
to achieve anything great,

713
00:33:39,830 --> 00:33:43,550
why would I need to use the Blade Tomb
to revitalize the divine sect?

714
00:33:43,550 --> 00:33:45,040
Shut your mouth.

715
00:33:45,160 --> 00:33:47,040
Surrender now.

716
00:33:47,590 --> 00:33:48,720
Gou Lingfeng!

717
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,350
Your martial skills...

718
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:52,350
You're clearing using

719
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:54,160
demonic skills!

720
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:56,190
What are you doing?

721
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:59,150
I'm doing what a hero should do.

722
00:34:00,550 --> 00:34:01,470
Stop!

723
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:03,840
Lingfeng!

724
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:08,590
Zhuge, Ying Dan?

725
00:34:08,590 --> 00:34:09,510
Lingfeng!

726
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:10,870
