730
00:34:22,440 --> 00:34:23,360
Gou Lingfeng.

731
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:25,710
You protected the Blade God

732
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:27,440
and captured Mr. Dao
from the demonic sect.

733
00:34:27,670 --> 00:34:29,030
As the vice chairman, I've decided

734
00:34:29,030 --> 00:34:31,030
to free you from imprisonment.

735
00:34:31,030 --> 00:34:32,360
Your sins are cleansed.

736
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:33,630
I'm free!

737
00:34:33,630 --> 00:34:36,190
I'll report this
to Chairman Wu Guangming.

738
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:39,310
You're still an Ox-rank hero

739
00:34:41,510 --> 00:34:42,560
of the association.

740
00:34:43,710 --> 00:34:45,190
Here's Eunuch Deng's decree.

741
00:34:45,590 --> 00:34:47,670
Gou Lingfeng's identity
has been verified,

742
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:49,440
not a demonic sect member.

743
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:50,880
That's obvious.

744
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:55,670
A few days ago,

745
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:57,190
I visited my godfather.

746
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:58,760
He said there have been

747
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,110
